For file names, module_filename.c
For function names, module_function_name.c

4space indentation

Compulsory comment in the beginning of every C/Header file in doxygen specified format
Compulsory comment for every global variable in doxygen specified format
Compulsory comment in the beginning of every method in doxygen specified format
Compulsory comment about every struct on top of it and for each of its member variable in doxygen specified format

For any logic exceeding 4 lines, good-to-have comments

No check-ins without review on any C/Header/Unit test files/documentation/README files
Compilation only using Makefile

